Company Overview of Executive Risk Indemnity, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Executive Risk Indemnity, Inc. offers property and casualty insurance services. The company was formerly known as Executive Re Indemnity Inc. and changed its name to Executive Risk Indemnity, Inc. in January 1995. The company was incorporated in 1977 and is based in Warren, New Jersey. Executive Risk Indemnity, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of Federal Insurance Company.


15 Mountain View RoadWarren, NJ 07059United StatesFounded in 1977



